snippet.textDisplay:
When I though Coke Studio can't have more to show ; they showed us glimpse of heaven. Yes! the world is heaven if we can truly embrace the message of love, hope, unity and universal brotherhood and that we all are the most beautiful creation of the same GOD. 
CSP has my heart❤
I am overwhelmed by the lyrics,  cinematography and music arrangement, melody and most importantly the pure intentions behind this rare work of ART.
This whole season is other worldly.
While I am excited what XULFI and CSP would have in store for us next season; i am gonna miss CSP as if it's departure time for someone who has been so close to me.
I known all this praise isn't  worth a fraction of all the hard-work you guys put in but still take all the standing ovations and all that I have said in your praise and all that I wanna say but just don't have the words to say
